180
00:16:51,121 --> 00:16:52,820
Mami. Mami.

181
00:16:55,531 --> 00:16:57,230
(Jang Seo Kyung)

182
00:17:22,190 --> 00:17:23,490
Ak ťa opustia raz,

183
00:17:24,361 --> 00:17:26,091
